
1. Install necessary OS packages.

If running Ubuntu:
$ sudo apt-get install $(< [this_directory]/PACKAGES.ubuntu)

If running CentOS:
TODO

2. Download and extract the OfficeMalScanner.zip file.

$ cd ~/
$ wget http://www.reconstructer.org/code/OfficeMalScanner.zip
$ sudo mkdir /opt/oms
$ cd /opt/oms
$ sudo unzip ~/OfficeMalScanner.zip

